&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.relexsolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/relex-greenhouse-banner-top.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;1280&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;ABOUT&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;RELEX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RELEX Solutions is a leading provider of cutting-edge retail optimization software. We offer our customers radically improved demand forecasting and supply chain optimization, which then can be leveraged into exponential benefits — optimizing store space, allocation, workforce, pricing and promotion strategies, all within our unified platform.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RELEX is trusted by leading brands including NTUC FairPrice, Estee Lauder, DFS, Coles Supermarket and Liquor and has offices across North America, Europe, and the Asia Pacific region.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RELEX Solutions is an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OUR SALES TEAM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Sales team believe in our potential and impact and are driven by the growth in our funding, our 100% success rate on implementation and the fact we are 100% referenceable. In return for their enthusiasm, we reward sales with different commission levels, genuine flexibility and an international workspace.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us as an&lt;strong&gt; Account Executive, Retail, in Japan &lt;/strong&gt;and this is some of what you’ll be doing:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Successful Sales Achievement: Meet&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;and exceed individual quarterly and annual quotas for contracts/revenue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prospecting:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Build and maintain a healthy pipeline of new business opportunities to meet quarterly and annual targets, including access to and alignment with the customer C-levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Pipeline Management: Maintain&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;an accurate Salesforce.com pipeline of all opportunities, white-space, contacts and account history and provide appropriate communication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Value-Based Selling: Deliver&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;an engaging value-based sales methodology and drive meaningful customer value for all respective stakeholders, including presenting the vision to the C-levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ethical Selling: Maybe&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;this should go without saying,&amp;nbsp;but RELEX is strongly centered around selling what we can deliver. It is at the core of our principles, and one reason we are roughly 100% customer referenceable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Cycle Management: Manage&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;all aspects of the sales cycle including solution development, deal term negotiation and contract closing process for new business opportunities within the territory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Negotiation: Negotiate&lt;/strong&gt; contracts and agreements to ensure that appropriate expectations are established, communicated and documented.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Focus: Work&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;collaboratively with internal teams to maintain 100% customer satisfaction, ensuring opportunities for additional business growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What will you bring to the table: -&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;5+ years of successful enterprise sales experience in supply chain planning within the Manufacturing industry focusing on tier one and two markets ($500M+).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Successful Track Record: Demonstrable&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;experience at complex sel

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.relexsolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/relex-greenhouse-banner-top.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;1280&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The RELEX team in APAC is growing, and we’re now looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Business Consultant &lt;/strong&gt;with business-level proficiency in English and Japanese to join our regional consulting team. This role is based in&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Tokyo, Japan&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Business Consultant, you’ll manage software implementation projects across the full project lifecycle in the field of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;retail supply chain&lt;/strong&gt;. You’ll be responsible for driving customer value through process design, configuration of RELEX solutions, training delivery, and business case realization. You will be part of a high-performing, international team, and have the chance to work closely with some of the most iconic&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Japanese retailers and wholesalers. &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;This is an ideal role for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;hands-on, analytical, and customer-oriented consultant&lt;/strong&gt; who wants to help businesses evolve their planning processes and make a real impact. You are autonomous, motivated, and eager to contribute to the continued growth of our APAC operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key responsibilities and accountabilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leading software implementation projects&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;and supporting customers in designing and optimizing their supply chain and retail planning processes.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Driving and participating in process development workshops (English and Japanese.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible in the Business Specification Design Document and User Stories for the backbone structure of it and for creating process maps and outlining the UI workflow designs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyzing KPIs and customer data to drive decisions and improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configuring RELEX tools based on customer-specific requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Delivering training to customer teams and providing ongoing support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensuring business case KPIs are tracked and achieved.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing change management and solution adoption with customer stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supporting pre-sales activities&lt;/strong&gt; such as scoping, value assessments, benefit analysis, and ROI case creation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acting as a &lt;strong&gt;trusted advisor&lt;/strong&gt; to clients by aligning RELEX best practices with the client’s strategic and operational objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Developing internal knowledge&lt;/strong&gt; through continuous learning and participation in RELEX product and methodology trainings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Occasionally participating in &lt;strong&gt;industry events&lt;/strong&gt; or internal strategic initiatives as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Onboarding of RELEX partner companies to successfully deliver RELEX projects in the future&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business-level proficiency in English and Japanese&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;3–5 years of experience&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;in supply chain planning, retail operations, or business consulting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Experience in retail or wholesale demand planning, forecasting, replenishment, or supply chain operations, ideally within sectors such as grocery, DIY, pharmacy, or other FMCG environments&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.relexsolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/relex-greenhouse-banner-top.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;1280&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development Representative&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;565&quot; data-end=&quot;931&quot;&gt;RELEX Solutions is growing rapidly, and we&#39;re looking for a high-performing Business Development Representative (BDR) to help accelerate pipeline growth across North America. This is an opportunity for an experienced SaaS sales professional to play a critical role in driving new business opportunities with some of the world&#39;s leading retailers and consumer brands.&lt;/p&gt;
