&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Targeted outbound demand generation: Identifying and contacting stakeholders in your target account list via emails, phone calls, and social media to drive awareness of how RELEX can help solve their unique challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage and qualify outbound and inbound sales leads with the objective of scheduling qualified meetings for the Sales team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cooperate closely with the regional sales team to support the growth of the sales pipeline through targeted prospecting activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research your list of target accounts, the key stakeholders within them, and the most relevant intent signals to craft and deliver personalized and compelling messaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support regional marketing initiatives, industry events, webinars, and follow-up campaigns to drive engagement and opportunity creation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We&#39;re looking for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1gw97o&quot; data-start=&quot;2712&quot; data-end=&quot;2841&quot;&gt;2+ years of Business Development, Sales Development, or inside sales experience within a SaaS, software, or technology company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1enxi3m&quot; data-start=&quot;2842&quot; data-end=&quot;2932&quot;&gt;Demonstrated success generating pipeline through outbound prospecting and cold outreach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;15vqbuc&quot; data-start=&quot;2933&quot; data-end=&quot;2996&quot;&gt;Experience engaging director-, VP-, and C-level stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ady0tx&quot; data-start=&quot;2997&quot; data-end=&quot;3116&quot;&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills with the ability to deliver compelling, business-focused messaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;19pbfwk&quot; data-start=&quot;3117&quot; data-end=&quot;3222&quot;&gt;Strong organizational skills and the ability to manage multiple prospecting initiatives simultaneously.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;17l3zd&quot; data-start=&quot;3223&quot; data-end=&quot;3318&quot;&gt;A proactive, resilient mindset with a track record of meeting or exceeding performance goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1lrs4x5&quot; data-start=&quot;3319&quot; data-end=&quot;3424&quot;&gt;Experience working in a collaborative sales environment and partnering closely with Account Executives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we consider as an advantage:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with B2B sales cycles and enterprise account-bas

