&lt;li&gt;Helping promote various events, physical and virtual, in advance, and following up post-event to qualify registrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll bring to the table&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in English, plus at least two of the following languages: Spanish, Arabic, German, or French.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to write and communicate effectively via email, phone, and social media.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confidence in communicating with senior executives at prospect accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An efficient and independent working style.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Eagerness to learn and a strong can-do attitude.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We work in a collaborative environment where knowledge sharing plays an important role in professional development. This will therefore be a hybrid role with office presence required 2 to 3 days per week.&lt;/p&gt;
