&lt;li&gt;Experience with Salesforce and Salesloft.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sales or Business Development experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in additional European languages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
