&lt;li&gt;Build, test, and validate platform configurations while partnering with customers through User Acceptance Testing to ensure solution readiness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop analytical queries on large datasets to deliver custom insights, KPI dashboards, and performance tracking that drive business case realization and system adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present findings and strategic recommendations to both operational teams and executive leadership, providing hands-on consulting on campaign evaluation, forecasting, and optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product and engineering teams to translate customer requirements into development roadmaps, and support sales efforts as a subject matter expert&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with global teams on international projects, sharing best practices and contributing to cross-regional knowledge transfer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
